{
  "texts": [
    "57 reported 100% rehabilitation program completion and improvements in upper extremity Fugl-Meyer assessment for all the patients in their study.",
    "In other studies with the same VRehab settings for all patients 25, 27, 65, the VRehab platform's effectiveness in delivering rehabilitation was not reported.",
    "However, the performance of the AI algorithms in predicting an outcome variable was reported.",
    "Ghorbel et al.",
    "58 investigated the correctness of exercises of the same patients with and without visual feedback on the computer and reported lower distances between correct exercises and patients' exercises when visual feedback was provided to patients."
  ]
}